#

Refreshing Watermelon Mint Juice

10 min
$5
60 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

vegangluten-freedairy-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Beverage

Tags:

beveragerefreshingsummer drink

Description

A refreshing and hydrating juice perfect for hot summer days, combining the sweetness of watermelon with a hint of mint.

Ingredients

  • seedless watermelon: 4 cups, cubed
  • fresh mint leaves: 1/4 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • water: 1/2 cup
  • honey (optional): 1 tablespoon
